snippet.title: Evercade -  Goodboy Galaxy/Witch n' Wiz & Demons of Asteborg/Astebros Dual Carts Trailer
snippet.description:
Two new dual cart collections come to Evercade this December with four great indie games! Save your home planet in Goodboy Galaxy, solve puzzles in Witch n' Wiz, explore the lands with Demons of Asteborg, and crawl the dungeons in Astebros!

Pre-order September 2023

Goodboy Galaxy/Witch n' Wiz: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/goodboy-galaxy-witch-n-wiz
Demons of Asteborg/Astebros:  https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/demons-of-asteborg-astebros/
Website: Evercade.co.uk
